<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="content-text">
        <h2>Local-First Philosophy</h2>
        <p>Your documents stay on your machine. No cloud sync required, no vendor lock-in. Writer uses your existing folder structure as the source of truth.</p>
        <p>Built with Tauri 2 for a lightweight, native experience. Rust backend handles file operations, indexing, and style checking with blazing speed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-image">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/500x375/262626/3ddbd9?text=Workspace+Browser" alt="Workspace browser showing folder structure" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section content-section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col reverse">
      <div class="content-text">
        <h2>Intelligent Writing Assistance</h2>
        <p>Style checking runs in real-time, highlighting potential improvements without being intrusive. Powered by aho-corasick pattern matching in Rust for instant feedback.</p>
        <p>Parts-of-speech highlighting helps you analyze sentence structure. Customize patterns to match your writing style guide.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-image">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/500x375/262626/ee5396?text=Style+Check" alt="Style check highlighting filler words" />
      </div>
